       Regulation of competence for genetic transformation in
       Streptococcus pneumoniae: expression of dpna a late competence gene
       encoding a DNA methyltransferase of the Dpnll restriction system.
       Mol. Microbiol. 35, 1089-1098 (2000). Medline Abstract

     * Lacks, S.A.,
       DNA uptake by transformable bacteria.
       In: Transport of molecules across microbial membranes, J.K.
