       Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, UK, pp. 136-168 (1999).

     * Tran, P.H., Korszun, Z.R., Cerritelli, S., Springhorn, S.S. and
       Lacks, S.A.,
       Crystal structure of the DpnM DNA adenine methyltransferase from
       the Dpnll restriction system of Streptococcus pneumoniae bound to
       S-adenosylmethionine.
       Structure 6, 1563-1575 (1998). Medline Abstract; PDB file: 2DPM

     * Lacks, S.A.
       DNA repair and mutagenesis in Streptococcus pneumoniae.
